Class GenProxyProcessor

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Processor

    @SupportedAnnotationTypes(value="com.gwtplatform.dispatch.annotation.GenProxy")
public class GenProxyProcessor
extends GenProcessor
    Processes GenProxy annotations.

    GenProxyProcessor should only ever be called by tool infrastructure. See Processor for more details.

    Author:
    Florian Sauter
